commit 7d83a155f0c4bf86bd6dfced1768c0a34add8f1b upstream

Add .prepare_fb and .cleanup_fb plane hooks into the drm_simple_kms.
These can be used by drivers to call ie. the drm_fb_cma_setup_fence()
helper.

